<subSubSection id="D6E265519272FFF9FF6FFE01FFFB1265" pageId="4" pageNumber="105" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="9E4736DA9272FFF9FF6FFE01FFFB1265" blockId="4.[178,1085,430,569]" pageId="4" pageNumber="105">
Comment: Confirmed records of 
<taxonomicName id="59F84D599272FFF9FD8BFE01FCDA119E" authorityName="EPPELSHEIM" authorityYear="1895" box="[598,710,430,451]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Orphnebius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="105" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hauseri">
<emphasis id="AC8CEAC89272FFF9FD8BFE01FCDA119E" box="[598,710,430,451]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="105">O. hauseri</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
were previously known only from Himachal Pradesh and 
<collectingCountry id="E6EF764A9272FFF9FE7EFE64FFC311BC" box="[419,479,459,481]" name="Nepal" pageId="4" pageNumber="105">Nepal</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation id="FA694B2B9272FFF9FE2DFE64FC6111BC" author="ASSING V" box="[496,637,459,481]" pageId="4" pageNumber="105" pagination="201 - 226" refId="ref13153" refString="ASSING V. (2009): New species and additional records of Lomechusini from the Palaearctic region (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae: Aleocharinae). - Stuttgarter Beitrage zur Naturkunde Serie A, Neue Serie 2: 201 - 226." type="journal article" year="2009">ASSING 2009</bibRefCitation>
). Previous records from 
<collectingCountry id="E6EF764A9272FFF9FCA3FE64FDA611BC" box="[894,954,459,481]" name="China" pageId="4" pageNumber="105">China</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry id="E6EF764A9272FFF9FC2CFE64FA2111BC" box="[1009,1085,459,481]" name="Taiwan" pageId="4" pageNumber="105">Taiwan</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation id="FA694B2B9272FFF9FF64FE47FF3311A0" author="PACE R" box="[185,303,488,509]" pageId="4" pageNumber="105" pagination="19 - 54" refId="ref13502" refString="PACE R. (2010): Thamiaraeini, Lomechusini, Oxypodini, Hoplandriini e Aleocharini di Taiwan (Coleoptera, Staphylinidae). - Bollettino del Museo Civico di Storia Naturale di Verona 34: 19 - 54." type="journal article" year="2010">PACE 2010</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="FA694B2B9272FFF9FEE1FE47FF6C11A3" author="PACE R" box="[316,368,488,510]" pageId="4" pageNumber="105" pagination="77 - 102" refId="ref13542" refString="PACE R. (2012): Biodiversita delle Aleocharinae della Cina: Lomechusini e Thamiaraeini (Coleoptera, Staphylinidae). - Beitrage zur Entomologie, Keltern 62 (1): 77 - 102." type="journal article" year="2012">2012</bibRefCitation>
) and even some from 
<collectingCountry id="E6EF764A9272FFF9FDBDFE47FC8011A3" box="[608,668,488,510]" name="Nepal" pageId="4" pageNumber="105">Nepal</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation id="FA694B2B9272FFF9FD70FE47FD3D11A3" author="PACE R" box="[685,801,488,510]" pageId="4" pageNumber="105" pagination="125 - 145" refId="ref13351" refString="PACE R. (1992): Aleocharinae nepalesi del Museo di Ginevra. Parte IV: Myrmedoniini (Coleoptera, Staphylinidae). - Revue Suisse de Zoologie 99 (1): 125 - 145." type="journal article" year="1992">PACE 1992</bibRefCitation>
) are undoubtedly based on misidentified material (see 
<bibRefCitation id="FA694B2B9272FFF9FE39FDA9FC9D1246" author="ASSING V" box="[484,641,517,539]" pageId="4" pageNumber="105" pagination="1 - 26" refId="ref13078" refString="ASSING V. (2006 a): A revision of the Palaearctic species of Orphnebius MOTSCHULSKY (Insecta: Coleoptera: Staphylinidae: Aleocharinae). - Entomological Problems 36 (2): 1 - 26." type="journal article" year="2006">ASSING 2006a</bibRefCitation>
, the section on 
<taxonomicName id="59F84D599272FFF9FC9AFDA9FDCE1247" authorityName="ASSING" authorityYear="2006" box="[839,978,517,539]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Orphnebius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="105" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="jumlaicus">
<emphasis id="AC8CEAC89272FFF9FC9AFDA9FDCE1247" box="[839,978,517,539]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="105">O. jumlaicus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, and the description of 
<taxonomicName id="59F84D599272FFF9FE99FD8CFFC51265" authorityName="Assing" authorityYear="2015" box="[324,473,547,568]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Orphnebius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="105" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="formosanus">
<emphasis id="AC8CEAC89272FFF9FE99FD8CFFC51265" box="[324,473,547,568]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="105">O. formosanus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
